Komposé README

Command line options:
  --nosystray               Don't show the systray icon
  --singleshot              Display the default view and exit (non daemon mode)

Keyboard shortcuts:
 Cancel                                      ESC
 Navigation between tasks 
   (within the view of the current desktop)  arrow keys, WASD keys or tab key
 Navigation between virtual desktops         Ctrl + arrow keys or WASD keys
 Selection of a window                       Return or Space